
initial setup:
    docker compose up --build

login to docker
    docker exec -it api /bin/sh

Setup dev mongo db 
    php artisan migrate

Run unittests
    login to docker and run this command
    ./vendor/bin/phpunit

Note:
    Usually lumen-app/.env is not added to the git repo. I added it here to make it a full working example.


Test Run instructions:

curl --location --request POST 'http://localhost:8000/person' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
  "name" : "John Will",
  "birthdate" : "2021-11-08 03:31:00",
  "timezone": "America/Los_Angeles"
}'


curl --location --request GET 'http://localhost:8000/person' 

